        <p><strong>These are projected estimates, not official IRS figures.</strong> For filing your 2025 return right now, use the <a href="/tax-brackets-2025" style="color:#92400e;font-weight:600;">confirmed 2025 brackets</a>. This page is for 2026 income planning only.</p>
